Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: 25? It would be a total of $113.95.

Speaker 2: $113.95?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Okay. I'll try that.

Speaker 1: Okay. And then when you're ready, I'll take your card, sir.

Speaker 1: One minute.

Speaker 2: No problem.

Speaker 1: 4-8-3-9.

Speaker 1: 4-8-3-9-5-0-3-5-7-5-4-9-0-8-7-7.

Speaker 1: 0-1-27.

Speaker 2: And the security code?

Speaker 1: This will ship out within a couple days.

Speaker 2: Your prescription is just going to get updated.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: I tried to do it over the internet.

Speaker 1: Yeah. It's not your fault.

Speaker 2: The way the system is set up, it wouldn't allow you.

Speaker 1: But now that I made the change, if you go on there,

Speaker 2: you should be able to order it as a refill if you want.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: All right. Thanks, sir.

Speaker 1: Bye.
